Introduction
Kristina von Rintelen currently works at the Museum für Naturkunde - Leibniz Institute for Research on Evolution and Biodiversity Science in Berlin, Germany. Kristina has biodiversity research projects on integrative biodiversity discovery in Indonesia and on taxonomy, evolution, and biogeography of Southeast Asian freshwater taxa (mainly atyid shrimps).
